{{Quote|Order, order!! This meeting of the Defense Committee will come to order! Thank you. Now, you're all aware of the trouble on the planet Onderon. But I'm afraid it's much worse than we suspected.|A meeting of the Defense Ministry during the [[Freedon Nadd Uprising]]|audio=Netus.flac|<ref name="Tales of the Jedi (audio)">[[Tales of the Jedi (audio drama)|''Tales of the Jedi'' audio drama]]</ref>}}
The '''Ministry of Defense''', also referred to as the '''Defense Committee''', was the agency responsible for oversight of the [[Republic Military/Legends|Republic Military]] and was headed by the [[Minister of Defense (Republic)|Minister of Defense]]. It was dissolved during the [[Ruusan Reformations/Legends|Ruusan Reformation]], along with its Minister.

During the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]], [[Netus]] was its head. During the [[Mandalorian Wars]], [[Koa Delko]] was Minister and [[Catronus Steffans]] was [[Defense Ministry Director for Public Information|Director for Public Information]]. [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Saul Karath]] and his forces were given information from the Defense Ministry that [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] forces were going to invade the [[Ottega system/Legends|Ottega system]]. After arriving, however, the Mandalorian forces disappeared, and it was revealed that it had been a trick by [[Zayne Carrick]] along with [[Cassus Fett]] in order for Karath to aid the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] in defeating [[the Crucible]].

